<section>
  <div class="bg-black text-white py-8">
    <div class="container mx-auto flex flex-col items-start md:flex-row my-12 md:my-24">
      <div class="flex flex-col w-full sticky md:top-36 lg:w-1/3 mt-2 md:mt-12 px-8">
        <p class="ml-2 text-yellow-300 uppercase tracking-loose">Recently added strategies</p>
        <p class="text-3xl md:text-4xl leading-normal md:leading-relaxed mb-2">Asset Allocation Strategies</p>
        <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-50 mb-4">
          Work on further asset allocation strategies continues: Discover the future of investing!
        </p>
        <a
          href="#"
          class="bg-transparent mr-auto hover:bg-yellow-300 text-yellow-300 hover:text-white rounded shadow hover:shadow-lg py-2 px-4 border border-yellow-300 hover:border-transparent"
        >
          Check out our strategies</a
        >
      </div>
      <div class="ml-0 md:ml-12 lg:w-2/3 sticky">
        <div class="container mx-auto w-full h-full">
          <div class="relative wrap overflow-hidden p-10 h-full">
            <div
              class="border-2-2 border-yellow-555 absolute h-full border"
              style="right: 50%; border: 2px solid #FFC100; border-radius: 1%;"
            >
            </div>
            <div
              class="border-2-2 border-yellow-555 absolute h-full border"
              style="left: 50%; border: 2px solid #FFC100; border-radius: 1%;"
            >
            </div>
            <div class="mb-8 flex justify-between flex-row-reverse items-center w-full left-timeline">
              <div class="order-1 w-5/12"></div>
              <div class="order-1 w-5/12 px-1 py-4 text-right">
                <p class="mb-3 text-base text-yellow-300">October, 2023</p>
                <h4 class="mb-3 font-bold text-lg md:text-2xl">Hybrid Asset Allocation</h4>
                <p class="text-sm md:text-base leading-snug text-gray-50 text-opacity-100">
                  Described by Wouter Keller and JW Keuning in 2023. It is based on momentum and the canary universe.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-8 flex justify-between items-center w-full right-timeline">
              <div class="order-1 w-5/12"></div>
              <div class="order-1 w-5/12 px-1 py-4 text-left">
                <p class="mb-3 text-base text-yellow-300">September, 2022</p>
                <h4 class="mb-3 font-bold text-lg md:text-2xl">Bold Asset Allocation</h4>
                <p class="text-sm md:text-base leading-snug text-gray-50 text-opacity-100">
                    Described by Wouter Keller in 2023. It is based on momentum and the canary universe. It considers three asset universes: offensive, defensive and “canary”.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-8 flex justify-between flex-row-reverse items-center w-full left-timeline">
              <div class="order-1 w-5/12"></div>
              <div class="order-1 w-5/12 px-1 py-4 text-right">
                <p class="mb-3 text-base text-yellow-300">August, 2023</p>
                <h4 class="mb-3 font-bold text-lg md:text-2xl">Protective Asset Allocation</h4>
                <p class="text-sm md:text-base leading-snug text-gray-50 text-opacity-100">
                    Described by Wouter Keller and JW Keuning in 2016. It use a simple dual-momentum model with a vigorous “crash protection”.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-8 flex justify-between items-center w-full right-timeline">
              <div class="order-1 w-5/12"></div>

              <div class="order-1 w-5/12 px-1 py-4">
                <p class="mb-3 text-base text-yellow-300">July, 2023</p>
                <h4 class="mb-3 font-bold text-lg md:text-2xl text-left">Classic 60/40</h4>
                <p class="text-sm md:text-base leading-snug text-gray-50 text-opacity-100">
                  The classic 60% stocks and 40% bonds allocation with monthly rebalancing.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <img
            class="mx-auto -mt-36 md:-mt-36"
            src="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/54521023/116968861-ef21a000-acd2-11eb-95ac-a34b5b490265.png"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
